Sentencas: The influence of the current collector on the performance of a hybrid direct carbon fuel cell (HDCFC), consisting of solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) with a molten carbonate-carbon slurry in contact with the anode, has been investigated using current-voltage curves.
Titulo: Hybrid Direct Carbon Fuel Cell Performance With Anode Current Collector Material

Sentencas: Four different anode current collectors were studied: Au, Ni, Ag, and Pt.
Titulo: Hybrid Direct Carbon Fuel Cell Performance With Anode Current Collector Material

Sentencas: It was shown that the performance of the direct carbon fuel cell (DCFC) is dependent on the current collector materials, Ni and Pt giving the best performance, due to their catalytic activity.
Titulo: Hybrid Direct Carbon Fuel Cell Performance With Anode Current Collector Material

Sentencas: Gold is suggested to be the best material as an inert current collector, due to its low catalytic activity.
Titulo: Hybrid Direct Carbon Fuel Cell Performance With Anode Current Collector Material
